Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 這裡是沖倉家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 啊 那個 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一個學校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 沖倉同學 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想…看到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 你現在就想看到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 現在就想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}總之我們見面說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去透子家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來我家的話你回去會很晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 這太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把事情做完就去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之後會有一位非常重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作品 對 我要做作品了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以不要進工房哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是要在吃飯前做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子真有熱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪喜歡的不是小柳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉同學要來我家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪和小柳都是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這一點從前以後都不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 就算我的心意不變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們之間的關係  也可能發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳…在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把小柳弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到未來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子的媒介是玻璃的原因就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來客人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我正忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐一直受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}馬上給您泡茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用了 沖倉同學馬上就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要對爸爸媽媽保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說是今天吃炸豬排哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}麻煩你過來 我倒像是要趕你回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是想看看小柳和小雪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被井美雪哉告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為…為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳注意到小雪有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來找我談心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}估計沒注意到的只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子看了他們的未來之後準備怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想找到不讓他們分開的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}先不說能不能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做什麼事都很拚命是你的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到這裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天大家會一起去爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉同學也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想你剛來這裡 是不是朋友還不怎麼多…什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我喜歡一個人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒注意到的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.10,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在還趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.72,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 有點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是也沒有其他方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.85,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}無論怎麼想都會覺得這個很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以啊 我不是說了女孩子是需要這個的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼爬山需要吹風機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是頭髮亂了該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說起來山上是沒有電的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}當然是充電式的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等你們好久了 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早～上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好 開始爬山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太慢了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}走錯了一條路 啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的 真的沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相信我這個關心弟弟的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是覺得危險的話 馬上打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.14,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 集合地點見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家 快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我呢 感覺見過小幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 可以叫你小幸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說到醫院 這裡的人都是去那家綜合醫院的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 那條掛鏈好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在哪裡買的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是別人送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 真有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼人 戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 是我喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哎呀 那傢伙很行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我家的那位不懂女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又很介意個子矮這種無所謂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是內心還是很善良的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要和他好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太期待今天 結果昨天沒睡著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天沖倉同學來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉同學就是那個轉學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看起來像是喜歡山的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是也邀請他來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我邀請他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是他說喜歡一個人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「孤高之人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我更喜歡和大家一起爬山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還有三十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝 坐車子很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然沒有坐過雲霄飛車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我想感覺也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雲霄…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼 到時候我會來接她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 多謝 姐姐也多小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來去如風的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在家裡就成颱風了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快看 是山哦 山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那邊是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}剛才爬的就是山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心情真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 那邊的山還有積雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那裡是日乃出山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我該做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}用這個打些水來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪裡能打到水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 你是最拿不了重東西的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉當然是負責搭帳篷的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也不用那麼費勁地找河流啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其實附近就有個接水的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有些話想問透子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 找到小溪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哇 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要和雪交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你在幹什麼呢 真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這裡鋪好了座位 可以看書哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去找那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她們確實太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是不知道在哪裡接水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其實旁邊就有條水管的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那傢伙大概也是個愛操心的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜歡炒麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我喜歡多加些紅薑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這裡就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}讓我大膽行動的是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過 我選的時間也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你是怎麼看雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說實話 嚇了一跳什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白之後一般不會說「多謝」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我說過這句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}話說 為什麼你會知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你會和雪交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不會交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然小雪很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我的戀愛感應器沒有發動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子身上好像沒有裝備這種東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒能讓你看到真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你們不會交往的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是透子喜歡雪的話 就更容易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我已經決定要支援你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想迷路都迷不了的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}慘叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快給老娘滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}順便 給老娘接一輩子水去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你那…一直…熱心…讀書的身影是如此迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在我眼中…宛若人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是詩什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 要放麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}燙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}水…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪裡要用水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}祐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}醍醐灌頂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}灌你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的著急了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.12,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吧 好好品味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}友情的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.64,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你手藝還挺不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.57,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}普普通通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.01,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我覺得真的很厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.12,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你誇得這麼直接感覺真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.52,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}別說噁心噁心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}證明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.60,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想把這個加到風道的菜單裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.64,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這想法不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.14,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是被採用了我一定會去吃的 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.24,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在我眼中 你就像人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我終於察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}手 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒有燙傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作為悉心照顧我的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不… 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在就可以看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…喜歡「幸」這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我覺得必須要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有比我更適合小雪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因為小雪是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒關係的 來 先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對了 我來的路上看到野豬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:45.30,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相當凶暴的 碰到的話裝睡可行不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.08,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不是熊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.42,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 是這樣來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 沒幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很快就收拾好了 沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回去的時候是直接送到家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:01.11,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哦 畢竟是有了動機 動作俐落多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 下次就在咖啡店見面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.29,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.63,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒～什～麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.94,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}別再用這種奇怪的說法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.90,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒～什～麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 真的要多小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:19.42,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好 沒問題 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.39,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 身體不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼 在碰到野豬之前下山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下山比上山更容易發生事故呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.79,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一直到家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 下山我走前面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}緊緊跟著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}致透子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天真的多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我會再聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}陽菜啊 要是被好朋友喜歡的人告白了 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒什麼怎麼辦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對告白的人只有喜歡不喜歡這兩個回答囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不愧是陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是 昨天那個哥哥沒有一起去登山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒有啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驅真是個奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳 是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感覺有點帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣嗎
